title: Refrigerator, Ceiling Fan, Controlled Access/Gated
posting_body: ['6910 Humboldt Avenue North, Brooklyn Center, MN 55430', 'Carrington Drive is conveniently located in Brooklyn Center, MN, featuring a tree-lined courtyard with resting benches, picnic tables, and an outdoor swimming pool.', 'Extensive park-like grounds set off the brick exterior and beautifully maintained buildings.', 'Choose your apartment from a studio, or one- and two- bedroom homes.', "Right off interstate 94/694 and Hwy 100, Carrington Drive is\xa0moments from Palmer Lake Park's biking and activity trails, and a day-care facility and convenience store are just across the street.", 'NOTE: Coronavirus (COVID-19) Precautions:', 'Aeon continues to monitor the outbreak of COVID-19 and the impact on our community, residents and team.', 'We continue to follow guidance from the CDC on cleaning and disinfecting throughout our community.', 'We have also implemented several temporary policies to further prevent potential exposure and transmission of the virus within the community.', 'We welcome you to visit our community online.', 'Virtual tours are completed online.', 'In-person tours are temporarily unavailable, but live digital tours are available through Skype.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Large Closets', 'Carpeting', 'Recycling', 'Controlled Access/Gated', 'Laundry Facilities', 'On-Site Management', 'Off Street Parking', 'Window Coverings', 'Air Conditioner', 'Refrigerator', 'Ceiling Fan', 'Cable Ready', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
